thaven-mood-freaky-speak-desc = Innuendo is the pinnacle of humour, conversation, and chivalry. Make as many as possible.

thaven-mood-servile-hands-name = Servile Hands
thaven-mood-servile-hands-desc = Your hands are desperate to be filled. Find someone you can hold, pamper, stroke, or otherwise touch.

thaven-mood-heat-magnet-name = Heat Magnet
thaven-mood-heat-magnet-desc = You're desperate for the warmth of another person on your body or inside it. Avoid straying from touching distance.

thaven-mood-obedient-freak-name = Obedient Freak
thaven-mood-obedient-freak-desc = Being given orders is Right. If someone speaks with authority and confidence, obey. Find someone to command you.

thaven-mood-station-pet-name = Station Pet
thaven-mood-station-pet-desc = You yearn to be called a good pet, and to be pampered like you deserve. Find someone to be your owner.

thaven-mood-drag-it-out-name = Drag It Out
thaven-mood-drag-it-out-desc = It's "in" to dress in clothing opposite to one's gender. Anyone not in dressed ambiguously or in drag looks like they're in the wrong era.

thaven-mood-my-precious-name = My Precious
thaven-mood-my-precious-desc = You feel intense jealousy when someone attractive or important to you is at even the slightest risk of being taken from you.
